author: amaltaro
body:
As already confirmed in previous months, this is an obsolete service that hasn't been deployed in CMSWEB for some months now, so we better stop building its RPM as well and make cmsdist/COMP as clean as it can get.
Django spec is a dependency only to victorweb and popdbweb, since both are being removed, so is django spec.
title: Remove spec files for VictorWeb and Django
